# Control-plane template for installed KBs

Template for the CLAUDE.md/AGENTS.md fragment generated when commonplace is installed into a project. The KB Goals section requires human input during installation. All other sections come from commonplace and can be regenerated on upgrade.

See [KB goals in always-loaded context guide inclusion decisions](kb/notes/kb-goals-in-always-loaded-context-guide-inclusion-decisions.md) for design reasoning.

